portainer

manage all your vps inside 1 portainer 

to do that you should install the script inside all vps as a docker so you can add them from add environment from main portainer to add them together 

نصب داکر ، داکر کومپوز و انجین ایکس پراکسی 
Docker, Docker Compose, Nginx Proxy, portainer


for install

mkdir docker && cd docker
wget https://github.com/OpiranClub/install_docker/blob/main/install_docker.sh && chmod +x install_docker.sh
./install_docker.sh

portainer address:

http://IPADDRESS:9000
or
https://DOMAIN:9000

also from nginx proxy manager you can add location to use it as :

https://DOMAIN


